      <answer>
        <p>
          Please, see
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="http://www.irian.biz/tobago-example-demo/">Demo</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          and especially the section for best practices:
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="http://www.irian.biz/tobago-example-demo/faces/best-practice/intro.jsp">
