          </a>
        </p>
      </answer>
    </faq>
    <faq id="hello-world">
      <question>Where can I find a "Hello World" example and a list of required
        jars?
      </question>
      <answer>
        <p>
          Please look at
          <a href="http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/myfaces/tobago/trunk/example/blank/">
